reviewText: I forgot just how silly this show was! When I was younger it was one of my favorites and I couldn't wait until it was going to be on. You can definitely see (especially in some of the more serious moments in the show)  why Will Smith has become the great actor he is today. It's great to hear the slang used that I had totally forgotten about!! The 90's were a great time!! If you liked the show then, I'm sure you'll still like it now! The price was great too! $19.99 for 2 seasons!! The DVD' s are in great shape as well as the cases. Definitely worth the money!! I'm not disappointed one bit.
summary: Still as funny as I remember!
